txt.en: This ornate spear is of a much higher quality than is usual for goblins. Perhaps it may hold a clue as to the origins of these Warg-riders. You should bring it to Gwilum at Barnavon.

'Indeed, this spear seems to be of particular quality... not at all like that of a coblun -- goblins as you call them. However, I'm not familiar with these decorations.\n\n'I will need to study this further.'
'Have you found any evidence as to the origins of the Warg-riders?'
You found an ornate spear upon the corpse of a goblin Warg-rider. The quality and make of the spear seemed unusual for a goblin.
Bring the ornate spear to Gwilum in Barnavon
Gwilum is at the gate to Lower Barnavon.\n\nYou should bring the spear you found to Gwilum.
